This template is true for the ESP12-F chipset. I read that there might be other chipsets, so please verify!

ARILUX LC-08 can be found usually as "Magic Home Mini WIFI Led controller" It is the RGB+CCT model from the many LC-0x type. The plastic casing is quite tight, you have to force it open.

Channels:
- GPIO4    Green  PWM2
- GPIO5    Red      PWM1
- GPIO14  Blue     PWM3
- GPIO12  WW      PWM4
- GPIO13  CW       PWM5